open](https://globalvoicesonline.org/wp-
content/uploads/2011/03/citesoleil.jpg)](http://yfrog.com/h0nr3cyj)

@melindayiti: "Small crowd at Cite Soleil voting bureau, already open". The
vast Cité Soleil slum is as one of the poorest and most dangerous areas in
Haiti.

